=== SSE Module ===
Has subscribers Map/Set: true
Has addSubscriber: true
Has removeSubscriber: true
Has broadcast: true
Has globalThis registry: true
Has station filter: true

=== POST /api/order SSE broadcast ===
Has broadcast on new order: true

=== useOrderStream ===
Has EventSource: true
Has station filter: true
Has onNewOrder callback: true

=== Station pages ===
Bar uses StationView: true
Bar station="bar": true
Kitchen uses StationView: true
Kitchen station="kitchen": true
Overview uses StationView: true
Overview station="all": true

=== Staff layout ===
Layout imports StaffNav: true
StaffNav has /staff/bar link: true
StaffNav has /staff/kitchen link: true
